strings: <voice_0x01000D58><se_low>King of tricks: Are these tears from Venus? Why won't she give it to him?
<voice_0x01000D59><se_low>January: avoid! Am I not understanding correctly? “Think” should be replaced with “Discover”. We have to play the right role.
<voice_0x01000D5A><se_low>January: Otherwise they think we did something special, no prizes!
